## Limitations

The analysis is based on secondary sources, which may not capture the full spectrum of individual experiences across different cultures and socio-economic backgrounds. Additionally, the perspectives provided are largely generalized and may not account for the nuances of personal growth and development that vary from person to person. Further research involving primary data collection could provide a more nuanced understanding of the transition from childhood to adulthood.